        <body>
            <pb n="1"/>
            <p rend="align(right)"><placeName>New York</placeName>
                <date>June 27th 5614</date>.</p>
            <p rend="indent(11)">
                <addressee>Rev Isaac Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
            <p>
                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>
            </p>
            <p>
                <add>שלום כנהוגי</add>
            </p>
            <p rend="align(right)">
                <persName role="author">Michael Light</persName>
                <placeName>42. Oliver<lb/>
                    <sic>st</sic></placeName>
            </p>
            <pb n="2"/>
            <p>
                <addressee>Rev. Isaac Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
            <p>
                <placeName>371 Walnut Street</placeName>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">
                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">Pa</p>
            <pb n="3"/>
            <p rend="align(right)"><placeName>New York</placeName>, <date>June 29, 1854</date>.</p>
            <p><sic><addressee>Rev. Isaac Lesser</addressee></sic>,
                    <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>,</p>
            <p>Peace, as usual, most honored friend:</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Please send an “Occident” to <persName>Mr. Joseph Levy</persName>,
                    <placeName>Honesdale,<lb/> Pa.</placeName> If you want to, <persName>Mr.
                    Levy</persName> will pay you the $3. in advance, but<lb/> there is no need for
                it. The man is reliable. I am surprised that<lb/> you have not replied to my last
                    <sic>latter</sic>, either to myself or to <persName>Mr.<lb/>
                    Michaelson</persName>. Even if the reply be a refusal, the said man wants
                to<lb/> have it, in order to come before the trustees with clean hands, that<lb/> he
                has written for it. I sent you my own and <persName>Michaelson's</persName> letter,
                    <sic>t</sic><lb/> through <persName>Frankel</persName>, <placeName>13 North
                    Street, Philadelphia</placeName>.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">With all respect, I sign in friendliness,</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)"><persName role="author">Michael</persName> son of <persName>Rabbi
                    Abraham Uri</persName></p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">
                <persName role="author">Michael Light</persName>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(4)">
                <placeName>42 Oliver Street</placeName>
            </p>
        </body>
